═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Auth: ApiKeyMiddleware reads "X-Api-Key" header,
matches ProjectEnvironment.ApiKey,
injects ProjectEnvironment into HttpContext.Items["Environment"].
Unauthorized → 401 JSON.

GET /api/client/features
  Header: X-Api-Key: {apiKey}
  Flow: Redis cache check → miss → load from DB (flags + group members) → cache 30s → return
  Response:
  {
    "environment": "production",
    "projectSlug": "my-project",
    "fetchedAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "flags": [
      {
        "name": "awesome-feature",
        "isEnabled": true,
        "description": "...",
        "targetMode": "SpecificUsers",
        "targetIdentifierType": "Email",
        "targetUserList": ["ali@co.com"],
        "groupMembers": []
      }
    ]
  }

POST /api/client/metrics
  Header: X-Api-Key: {apiKey}
  Body: { "flagName": "...", "wasEnabled": true, "userId": "u1" }
  Action: upsert FlagEvaluationMetric (5-min bucket), update flag.LastSeenAt

